  "name": "Abyssal Claws",
  "permission": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you can grow claws as a free action. These claws are treated as natural weapons, allowing you to make two claw attacks as a full attack action using your full base attack bonus. These attacks deal 1d4 points of damage each (1d3 if you are Small) plus your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Strength</a>&nbsp;modifier. At 5th level, these claws are considered magic weapons for the purpose of overcoming&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Damage-Reduction-DR-\" rel=\"nofollow\">DR</a>. At 7th level, the damage increases by one step to 1d6 points of damage (1d4 if you are Small). At 11th level, these claws become&nbsp;flaming weapons, each dealing an additional 1d6 points of fire damage on a successful hit. You can use your claws for a number of rounds per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier. These rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>",
